title: Free TeamSpeak for OCE oceteamspeak.com
body:
**Free TeamSpeak for OCE oceteamspeak.com**

Feel free to use this as you wish and please share it around!!!

We can provide rank up to regular after 3hrs of use that will allow you to have the options to create temp channels for you and your friends, so your free from the trolls (if any join that is) **edit all users can make temp channels now**
Also can provide Permanent Channels with password for those who ask (msg Yeahman on TeamSpeak)

(Non profit) Just want to give back to OCE

Happy Holidays :D

replies.body: This is super cool! Thanks for sharing ^_^
How long is the actual server for? My group and I could use a teamspeak area, I'd also love to help out the community :)
server will be up for a very long time years at that :D
Yay free team speak to use
